I understand if you think it may modify too many things here, but I'd prefer an actual `Assume` instead of the comment:
```suggestion
    CoinsCachePair* Next() const noexcept
    {
        Assume(IsDirty());
        return m_next;
    }
```

(same for `Prev`)

